35:46.937 --> 35:49.898
OF YOUR LIFE SAVINGS.

35:49.940 --> 35:52.358
YEAH,

35:49.940 --> 35:52.358
WE TOOK IT OUT OF YOUR ACCOUNT.

35:52.400 --> 35:56.321
YES, ALL OF IT.

35:52.400 --> 35:56.321
I'LL TAKE ALL OF IT.

