WELL, THAT --

36:04.997 --> 36:08.000
THAT COULD BE ANYTHING.

36:08.041 --> 36:09.001
I DON'T KNOW.

36:09.042 --> 36:10.794
NATHAN FORD IS A VERY BAD MAN.

36:10.836 --> 36:13.880
I THINK WE BETTER GET

36:10.836 --> 36:13.880
SOME WARRANTS AND TALK

36:10.836 --> 36:13.880
TO THESE JUDGES.

36:13.922 --> 36:16.842
THEY, UH,

36:13.922 --> 36:16.842
THEY COULD BE IN TROUBLE.

