GIVE ME YOUR HANDS.

36:18.927 --> 36:20.219
-LET'S GO.

36:18.927 --> 36:20.219
-TELL ME, MR. WORTH,

36:20.261 --> 36:22.305
WHAT KIND OF GUY MAKES MONEY

36:22.347 --> 36:24.557
LETTING GUILTY PEOPLE

36:22.347 --> 36:24.557
OUT OF PRISON, HUH?

36:24.599 --> 36:25.642
GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

36:25.684 --> 36:27.853
HEY, HEY!

