WHAT HAVE YOU DONE

36:48.081 --> 36:49.582
TO MY APARTMENT?

36:49.624 --> 36:51.835
I'M THE LANDLORD,

36:49.624 --> 36:51.835
AND THIS PLACE WAS VACANT.

36:51.877 --> 36:53.170
WE NEEDED AN OFFICE.

36:53.211 --> 36:55.088
NOW, I GOT STAGGERED FLIGHTS

36:53.211 --> 36:55.088
ON AIR FRANCE.

36:55.130 --> 36:56.589
NATE, I PUT YOU ON A TRAIN

36:55.130 --> 36:56.589
TO NEW YORK,

36:56.631 --> 36:57.883
THEN YOU FLY OUT ON AIR URUGUAY.

