AIR URUGUAY?

36:57.924 --> 36:59.425
WHAT ARE YOU TAL--

36:59.467 --> 37:01.344
YEAH, YOUR PASSPORT HAS YOU

36:59.467 --> 37:01.344
AS JUAN FORD, COFFEE MERCHANT.

