NOW, LOOK, WE ALL RENDEZVOUS

37:01.386 --> 37:05.015
IN PARIS AND...

37:06.599 --> 37:10.645
BUONA SERA, SIGNORE FORD.

37:18.570 --> 37:20.072
I WOULD PREFER WINE.

37:20.113 --> 37:22.407
GOOD FOR YOU.

37:22.448 --> 37:24.409
[ SIGHS ]

37:26.619 --> 37:27.954
HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT --

37:27.996 --> 37:29.664
SOME THIRD PARTY WAS AT PLAY?

37:29.706 --> 37:32.042
COME ON, THE ENTIRE PLAN

37:32.084 --> 37:34.252
DEPENDED ON WORTH FINDING OUT

37:32.084 --> 37:34.252
SOPHIE WAS BENT.

37:34.293 --> 37:35.503
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO PANIC.

37:35.545 --> 37:36.922
I MEAN, WE WERE ABOUT

37:35.545 --> 37:36.922
TO TIP HIM OFF, BUT --

37:36.963 --> 37:39.549
I CALLED HIM FIRST.

37:40.967 --> 37:42.427
AHH.

37:42.468 --> 37:46.223
LOOK, A GUY WITH MY REP WHO

37:42.468 --> 37:46.223
STINGS CORRUPT MILLIONAIRES

