I MEAN, THIS WASN'T

37:53.479 --> 37:55.232
JUST A JAILBREAK, WAS IT?

37:55.273 --> 37:56.649
IT WAS AN AUDITION.

37:56.691 --> 38:01.654
YOU ARE AS GOOD AS THEY SAY.

38:01.696 --> 38:03.489
POSSIBLY TOO GOOD.

