DAMIEN MOREAU?

38:13.499 --> 38:16.086
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

38:13.499 --> 38:16.086
NOBODY TOUCHES MOREAU!

38:16.128 --> 38:17.754
NATE, MOREAU FINANCES

38:16.128 --> 38:17.754
THE SICILIANS,

38:17.796 --> 38:20.132
THE RUSSIAN MAFIA,

38:17.796 --> 38:20.132
THE COLOMBIAN CARTELS.

38:20.173 --> 38:21.633
YEAH, HE MOVES MONEY

38:20.173 --> 38:21.633
FOR THE NORTH KOREAS,

38:21.674 --> 38:25.344
STOLEN ARTIFACTS FOR IRAQ,

38:21.674 --> 38:25.344
NUCLEAR MATERIALS FOR IRAN.

38:25.386 --> 38:26.596
MOREAU IS  THE  BIG BAD.

38:26.638 --> 38:29.224
HE IS THE CENTRAL BANK

38:26.638 --> 38:29.224
FOR INTERNATIONAL CRIME.

