38:36.648 --> 38:38.233
YOU'RE NOT THE POLICE.

38:38.275 --> 38:40.735
I'M NOT THE POLICE.

38:40.777 --> 38:44.281
MOREAU BUYS THE POLICE.

38:40.777 --> 38:44.281
HE BUYS POLITICIANS.

38:44.322 --> 38:47.033
AND NO LAW ENFORCEMENT

38:44.322 --> 38:47.033
OR INTELLIGENCE AGENCY

38:47.075 --> 38:48.326
CAN TOUCH HIM.

