39:00.880 --> 39:03.049
GUYS, GUYS, GUYS!

39:03.091 --> 39:05.510
JUST WAIT A SECOND.

39:03.091 --> 39:05.510
THIS IS NOT A JOB.

39:05.551 --> 39:07.220
IF YOU BRING ME

39:05.551 --> 39:07.220
DAMIEN MOREAU,

39:07.262 --> 39:09.681
YOU CAN WALK AWAY

39:07.262 --> 39:09.681
AND NOBODY WILL CHASE YOU.

39:09.722 --> 39:11.683
[ SIGHS ]

39:23.153 --> 39:25.363
AND IF I FAIL?

39:25.404 --> 39:27.406
YOU CAN STAY IN MY PRISON

39:25.404 --> 39:27.406
IN ROME.

39:27.448 --> 39:29.659
THICK WALLS

39:27.448 --> 39:29.659
A THOUSAND YEARS OLD.

39:29.701 --> 39:33.038
AND WE STILL USE CHAIN

39:29.701 --> 39:33.038
FOR SUCH A BAD MAN.

