WHAT ABOUT MY TEAM?

39:35.748 --> 39:37.792
THEY LEAD DANGEROUS LIVES.

39:37.834 --> 39:40.670
THIEVES DIE ALL THE TIME.

39:43.048 --> 39:45.717
NOW THAT

39:43.048 --> 39:45.717
YOU SHOULD NOT HAVE SAID.

39:45.758 --> 39:49.012
I DON'T KNOW.

39:49.054 --> 39:53.308
YOU SEEM HIGHLY MOTIVATED.

