RIGHT, SO WHAT WE DO IS

40:24.214 --> 40:26.132
WE DO LIKE WE'VE

40:24.214 --> 40:26.132
ALWAYS DONE IN THE PAST,

40:26.174 --> 40:27.926
IS WE DO JOBS THAT HELP PEOPLE.

40:27.967 --> 40:30.095
